{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, we employed a snowballing search strategy to further extend and validate our results.",
    "The selection process involved multiple stages to ensure rigorous evaluation and minimise selection bias.",
    "Initially, the first author filtered the tools based on the description in the repositories.",
    "Next, all authors participated in a more thorough review of the shortlisted tools.",
    "In cases where information was unclear or missing, the first author contacted the tool developers directly through email or online interviews."
  ]
}